Enter a list of paths on which IP addresses will be checked. For example, to check IP addresses on this page, you would enter admin/config/people/restrict_ip. All paths not included here will not be checked. Do not include domain names. The '*' character is a wildcard. An example path is /user/* for every user page.

Enter a list of paths that will be allowed regardless of IP address. For example, to not check IP addresses on this page, you would enter admin/config/people/restrict_ip. All paths not included here will be checked. Do not include domain names. The '*' character is a wildcard. An example path is /user/* for every user page.
